platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: If you play basketball, HomeCourt can change your game for the better. It uses your iPhones and iPads cameras and sensors plus its own proprietary AI technology to analyze your jumperno extra hardware or gadgets required. Just set up the app, point your device toward the court, shoot the ball, and get real-time shot tracking and analysis.
Change your basketball game for the better. Using just your iPhone or iPads camera and sensors with the apps own AI tech, you can get real-time analysis of your shots  no extra gadgets required.
